NAME
    wc - word, line, and character count

SYNOPSIS
    wc [-lwc] [file]

DESCRIPTION
    Counts lines, words, and characters in a file or stdin.
    By default, all three counts are displayed.

OPTIONS
    -l      Count lines only
    -w      Count words only
    -c      Count characters only

EXAMPLES
    wc /tmp/file.txt
        Show lines, words, and characters

    wc -l /tmp/file.txt
        Count lines only

    find . | wc -l
        Count number of files found

    cat file | wc -w
        Count words in file

SEE ALSO
    cat, grep
